articles.title: About
articles.description: Some additional details about the blog
articles.contents:
This blog was created as part of the class project for EDLD 654 in Applied Machine Learning in Educational Data Science, taught by Prof. Daniel Anderson and Prof. Joseph Nese at the University of Oregon.
The authors of the blog are doctoral students at the University of Oregon:
Asha Yadav, Special Education
Alejandra, Prevention Science
Chris Ives, Special Education
